{
  "name": "Corpse Bomb",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/death.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may make any of your ghost strikes against any corpse capable of being raised as a skeleton or zombie, or against any corporeal mindless undead under your control. The corpse explodes in a 20-foot radius, affecting all creatures in range as if they had been struck by the chosen ghost strike; if the ghost strike does not allow a saving throw, creatures affected are allowed a Reflex save to negate its effects.</p>\n<p>The corpse or undead collapses and is destroyed; it cannot be reanimated or targeted by another Corpse Bomb.</p>\n",
